quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  61,1,Zamin-o-aasman ki her her cheez Allah Taalaa ki paki biyan kerti hai aur wohi ghalib hikmat wala hai
  61,2,Aey eman walo! Tum woh baat kiyon kehtay ho jo kertay nahi
  61,3,Tum jo kertay nahi uss ka kehna Allah Taalaa ko sakht na pasand hai
  61,4,Be-shak Allah Taalaa unn logon say mohabbat kerta hai jo uss ki raah mein saff basta jihad kertay hain goya woh seesa pilaee hui emaarat hain
  61,5,Aur (yaad kero) jabkay musa ney apni qom say kaha aey meri qom kay logo! Tum mujhay kiyon sata rahey ho halankay tumhen (ba khoobi) maloom hai kay mein tumhari janib Allah ka rasool hun pus jab woh log tairhay hi rahey to Allah ney unn kay dilon ko (aur) tairhaa ker diya aur Allah Taalaa na farman qom ko hidayat nahi deta
  61,6,Aur jab marium kay betay essa ney kaha aey (meri qom) bani israeel! Mein tum sab ki taraf Allah ka rasool hun mujh say pehlay ki kitab toraat ki mein tasdeeq kerney wala hun aur apney baad aaney walay aik rasool ki mein tumhen khushkhabri sunaney wala hun jin ka naam ahmed hai phir jab woh unn kay pass khuli daleelen laye to yeh kehney lagay yeh to khula jadoo hai
  61,7,Uss shaks say ziyada zalim aur kaun hoga jo Allah per jhoot (iftra) bandhay halankay woh islam ki taraf bulaya jata hai aur Allah aisay zalimon ko hidayat nahi kerta
  61,8,Woh chahtay hain kay Allah kay noor ko apney mun say bujha den aur Allah apney noor ko kamal tak phonchaney wala hai go kafir bura manen
  61,9,Wohi hai jiss ney apney rasool ko hidayat aur sacha deen dey ker bheja takay ussay aur tamam mazaahib per ghalib ker dey agar cheh mushrikeen na khush hon